Package: MIRDD
Title: Diagnostic Tool by Multiple Imputation for Regression
        Discontinuity Designs
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Masayoshi", "Takahashi", 
                  email = "mtakahashi615@g.chuo-u.ac.jp", 
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Estimates local average treatment effects based on regression 
    discontinuity designs (RDD) and multiple imputation regression 
    discontinuity designs (MIRDD). It provides diagnostic tools for RDD 
    by comparing results with those from MIRDD, as proposed in 
    Takahashi (2023) <doi:10.1080/03610918.2021.1960374>.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
